quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,"Mi woondiri e Tiin(Жҙibbe)(nebbam) e jaytuun."
  95,2,"E fella Tuuri Siiniina."
  95,3,"E ndi lesdi koolii ndi."
  95,4,"Min tagii neЙ—Й—o e mba'adi Й“urndi fortaade e feewde."
  95,5,"Refti min ndutti mbo to Й“uri le'esЙ—ude."
  95,6,"Si wona Й“een goЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙi Й—iin, hino woodani Й“e njoЙ“di ndi taЖҙondirta."
  95,7,"Hol ko yeddatma Гұalawma njobdi caggal Й—uum."
  95,8,"Mbele Alla wona Й“urЙ—o nuunЙ—ude e ГұaawooЙ“e Й“e."
